The '''Mark VII power crossbow''' was a [[Crossbow/Legends|crossbow]] made by [[Malkanthi]]. It had an over-stock-mounted magazine capable of holding five crossbow bolts which were each tipped with barbed heads or injector heads filled with tranquilizers. The crossbow was favored by the [[Bounty hunter/Legends|bounty hunter]] [[Boddu Bocck]] for hunting [[Sentience/Legends|sentients]] and wild game.

